reviewText: Killer buy great quality I awant them all !!

This collection is of the first 4 tods it was great to relive the matches and was even more great to see my good friend nick mondo,
i own the white pants he wore in tod 2 its a cool story to tell when im watching with my friends

First of all this set is incrediable first four tournament of deaths spanning weed whackers lite tubes panes of glass big ones , barbed wire ladders etc everything u could imagine and blood coming out of every where the DVD quality is good cuz these shows are a little outdated compared to the new czw shows any hardcore wrestling fan would love this 5 stars loved it and plan to add more to my 200 + collection
